data.description: Stunning 4-bedroom 3-bathroom beautifully design modern feature home built less than 2 years ago, this home combines style, comfort, convenience in a sought-after neighborhood. Generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for your family. Beautifully designed bathrooms offer a touch of luxury and relaxation. The kitchen features state-of-the-art appliances, granite countertops, solid wood cabinets, ample storage space. Enjoy a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining, and living areas, perfect for daily living and entertaining. Premium wood style tile flooring adds elegance and durability. Step outside to the oversize backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and activities. Energy-efficient features, including modern insulation and appliances. Situated in a friendly neighborhood with access to excellent schools, shopping, restaurants. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a home with all the upgrades and features.
